LAGOS  – Arik Air has introduced a sales promotion that will enable its frequent flyer programme, Affinity Wings, members to purchase miles for traveling across the airline’s domestic network. A statement by Mr. Adebanji Ola, Communications Manager, Arik Air, the promo is tagged: ‘Buy Miles & Fly’ and it is targeted at new and existing Arik Affinity Wings members who can buy miles to fly to any of the airline’s destinations in the economy class cabin and earn additional 50 per cent bonus miles. The statement hinted that the promotion is available for sale from April 1, 2022 for travel between April 15 and May 15, 2022. The statement quoted Capt. Roy Ilegbodu, the Chief Executive Officer, Arik Air as saying that its products had always made life easier for its passengers. He said: “We value our customers and that explains why they are always the focal point of our operations. Our products are designed to make travel easy and convenient for them.”